title: An Upscale High-Rise in Turtle Creek Area**Washer/Dryer Inc**
posting_body: ['A New Luxury High-Rise in the Prestigious Turtle Creek Area close to Uptown, Victory Park, Oaklawn, and Downtown Dallas.', 'Convenient Location and Only Two Blocks From The Katy Trail, Shopping, Dining, and Entertainment at Your Door Step.', 'Enjoy the Luxury of White Quartz Countertops and Stainless Steel Appliances in the Kitchen.', 'Wood Floors, Walk-In Closets, Relaxing Garden Tubs, with Washer and Dryer Included in Your Luxury Apartment Home.', 'This Property has a Variety of Floorplans to Choose From.', 'Amenities Include a Resort Style Swimming Pool with Panoramic Views, a Dog Park, State of the Art Fitness Center, Plus So Much More.', 'Parking Garage and Elevators!', 'Great Management and Staff.', 'Please Call Jacquelyn with Dash Realty for More Information at', 'show contact info', '!', '**12 Month Lease or Longer, No Corporate Leases, and No Sublease**']
